descriptionHtml:
This is my own product. Its race is Vampire Dark Elf. I used [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/25373/?][color=#ff0000][size=4]Original Vampire Races[/size][/color]
[/url] by [color=#ff00ff]Loshirai14[/color]. This is the requirement to have Vampire Dark Elf Race. Thanks for his work!

We all know that it is difficult to create a beautiful dark elf face. I spent one week to finish my character face preset, 90 percent of work is done with sculpt button of Racemenu. I really thanks [color=#ff00ff]expired6978[/color] for his uploading [color=#ff0000][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624/?][size=4]RaceMenu[/size][/url][/color]. And i did not use any eyebrow, eyeball or any other parts of face mods. These parts i all choose default option provided by the original game.  Another mod i selected is [color=#ff0000][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/42049/?][size=4]Porcelain Pale Vampire Skin For Females[/size][/url][/color] by [color=#ff00ff]MissShazira[/color]. Thanks for his hard work. But you can still choose your own favorite skin texture. I used this mod [color=#ff0000][url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/57179/?][size=4]Female Hairstyles with Physics[/size][/url][/color] by [color=#ff00ff]Fuse00[/color]. I highly recommend this hairstyle for all of you. Its such an excellent mod by his hard working. Any body parts size if you don't like, you can choose body scale in racemenu to change. The armor and panty i wear is from [url=http://skyrimmodshighlights.blogspot.co.uk/2017/03/karlstein-cbbe-bodyslide.html]Karlstein full CBBE HDT[/url][size=4] [/size][size=2]and i am sorry that i cannot find author's name of this armor[/size]. And scarf and boots belong to [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/59202/?#][size=4]Sotteta Necromancer Outfit UNP[/size][/url]
 by [color=#ff00ff]nsk13[/color]. Thanks both of them for their high quality armors.

I took photos at different times of a day, such as dusk, night and daytime and also in racemenu interface just to show the different effect of sun lights.
author: Dong Zijie
